title: Ep. 591 - The Democrat Party Is The Most Anti-Child, Anti-Family Political Party In History
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, I will explain why no competent parent, especially of young children, can vote Democrat. Also Five Headlines including California’s attempts to tell their residents how many family members they may have over for Thanksgiving, where on their property they can meet with them, and how long they may stay together. Plus our Daily Cancellation and much more.
